                    <div2> 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b01"/>大魏永安三年歲次庚戌七月甲戌十一日□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b02"/>夫大聖慈隆。演化脩導。善業顯彰。倉生咸慕。曠代遵
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b03"/>崇。<note n="0078001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30560;＝虛【中研院】</note><app n="0078001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30560;</rdg></app>空&CB07099;&CB00515;。雖<note n="0078002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30561;＝冥【中研院】</note><app n="0078002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30561;</rdg></app>運不弔。真容凝位。是故 
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b04"/>釋□□生。以<note n="0078003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30318;＝&CB30397;【中研院】</note><app n="0078003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">&CB30397;</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30318;</rdg></app><note n="0078004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30562;＝權【中研院】</note><app n="0078004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30562;</rdg></app>曜。是以形教之興。敷沾有氣之
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b05"/>□□□影念貌遺像。但雙等。規奉玄門。幼染繢服。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b06"/>□□□巖岳寄氣。松石自慨。&CB01780;□返掌蹉跌又□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b07"/>□□□命如朝露。<note n="0078005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30563;＝仰【中研院】</note><app n="0078005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">仰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30563;</rdg></app><note n="0078006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30564;＝勸【中研院】</note><app n="0078006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">勸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30564;</rdg></app>師僧同<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">學</unclear>　衣&CB00425;
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b08"/>□□□四背。減妻子之珍。分於末代□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b09"/>□□餘人。咸自開悟。建　釋迦石像
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b10"/>□□薩兩師子。并天宮一區。起永安□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b11"/>功□□月十一日營訖。妙體沖邃。容貌澄相
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b12"/>光曜　<note n="0078007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30565;＝邊【中研院】</note><app n="0078007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30565;</rdg></app>外。<note n="0078008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30563;＝仰【中研院】</note><app n="0078008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">仰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30563;</rdg></app>為
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b13"/>皇帝　陛下。群遼百<note n="0078009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30566;＝辟【中研院】</note><app n="0078009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">辟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30566;</rdg></app>。中宮內外。師僧父母。因緣眷
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b14"/>屬。善<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">友</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">知</unclear>識。<note n="0078010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30567;＝逮【中研院】</note><app n="0078010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">逮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30567;</rdg></app>及七世。一切&CB07099;<note n="0078011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30565;＝邊【中研院】</note><app n="0078011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30565;</rdg></app>眾生。願沾　　速
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b15"/>成正覺。□同斯福　　大像邑都唯那比丘道陰
                            <lb ed="I" n="0078b16"/>□□□大像邑主前廣業寺主比丘慧雙<note n="0078012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30568;＝率【中研院】</note><app n="0078012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">率</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30568;</rdg></app>造
